Suite of programs to perform calculations with the Lipkin-Meshkov-Glick (LMG) model

H. J. Lipkin, N. Meshkov, and A. J. Glick, Nucl. Phys. 62, 188 (1965).
H. J. Lipkin, N. Meshkov, and A. J. Glick, Nucl. Phys. 62, 199 (1965).
H. J. Lipkin, N. Meshkov, and A. J. Glick, Nucl. Phys. 62, 211 (1965).

using a simplified model Hamiltonian

H = (1-xi) n - (4 xi/N) J_z^2 + 2 delta J_z

Note that LAPACK95 interface to the LAPACK library is needed to perform
model Hamiltonian diagonalization.

by Currix 

The program user's guide can be found in the doc directory in pdf,
html, and txt formats.

